{"title":"永恒的召唤","authors":["卢祖品"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":1,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"永恒的召唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卢祖品"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一出跌宕起伏的人间喜剧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰轰烈烈地开场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中华民族大梦初醒的时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而春天则从此"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长驻这块古老的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望的本质是稚嫩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿望总在不屈不挠地生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路上有旅人日夜赶路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车轮牛轭嘎嘎作响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊起的飞鸟重新辨认"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远海远山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呆滞的眼神恢复丰富的表"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是岔路修成林荫道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葛洲坝炫耀三峡夕阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凡是期待都令人焦灼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽宏的季节伴着紧张劳作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平地一声春雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后立即腾起阵阵沙烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪与世纪相互召唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一代的事情我们担当"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨上坐骑昂首远去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝着遥远的天边的地平线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州大地早该枝繁叶茂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全部谈笑注入缕缕芳香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工棚里散着混合气味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别忘了赶明儿早早起床"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海喜欢清晨的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随风吹向四面八方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消瘦的城市丰满起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝色的波涛日夜拍打悬崖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁都爱海不尽是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月下丝绸般闪光的波浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更爱怦然轰然的涛声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩击昏睡的灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱逐虚空的幻影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮汐交替"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流星留一道闪光的轨迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快夯好平实的基地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也让黄土迷蒙的高原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换上新世纪的披肩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能愧对祖国河山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一块烈火焚烧的石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都必须精读"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士临刑时的呼喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是最可宝贵的遗产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天发出永恒的召唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白热的焰火无色而透明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往前走迈动坚定的步伐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把历史的樊篱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一一踏平"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}